<item>
    <title>Elori Saxl, Henry Solomon - Seeing Is Forgetting</title>
    <link>http://usefulalgorithm.github.io/posts/2026-04-04-seeingisforgetting-elorisaxlhenrysolomon.html</link>
    <description><![CDATA[<article>
    <section class="header">
        Posted on April  4, 2026
        
        <br>
        
        Tags: <a title="All pages tagged &#39;2026&#39;." href="/tags/2026.html" rel="tag">2026</a>, <a title="All pages tagged &#39;music&#39;." href="/tags/music.html" rel="tag">music</a>, <a title="All pages tagged &#39;ambient&#39;." href="/tags/ambient.html" rel="tag">ambient</a>, <a title="All pages tagged &#39;minimalism&#39;." href="/tags/minimalism.html" rel="tag">minimalism</a>
        
    </section>
    <section>
        <p><img src="https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a1502137488_1x1_700.avif" /></p>
<p>極簡風的合成器 + 中音薩克斯風合奏專輯。可以聽得出來兩個人音樂取向上的差別：負責合成器的 Elori Saxl ，決定了歌曲的基調是平緩、非常有沈浸感的環境音樂，但 Henry Solomon （洛杉磯爵士大腕，好像吹過 Miley Cyrus）的演奏方式卻非常即興導向，信手拈來、旋律感十足的演奏，配上非常多的殘響。喜歡 cosmic jazz 或 Nala Sinephro 的人應該也會蠻喜歡這張的。</p>
<hr />
<p>Fav tracks: Reverence, Raindrop, A Thousand Steps, Heart, Seeing is Forgetting</p>
<p>Score: 8.4/10</p>
<p>Release date: 2026-02-06</p>
<p>Labels: True Panther Sounds</p>
    </section>
</article>
]]></description>
    <pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:00:00 UT</pubDate>
    <guid>http://usefulalgorithm.github.io/posts/2026-04-04-seeingisforgetting-elorisaxlhenrysolomon.html</guid>
